message.content: cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.ET - The paper proposes a deep learning-based system for fault analysis and power generator selection in solar power systems, indicating a strong focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The system also involves optimization and control of power grids, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses issues related to renewable energy sources, which could potentially fall under energy (cs.ET).
